CLARK:
About how long were you out of the pool?

01:00:41.670 --> 01:00:43.000
- Uh…
- Not long.

01:00:43.090 --> 01:00:45.420
Time it takes to make cookies.

01:00:45.500 --> 01:00:46.790
Hmm.

01:00:46.880 --> 01:00:49.040
Was there marijuana involved?

01:00:49.960 --> 01:00:51.880
Yes, but I-I have a card.

01:00:51.960 --> 01:00:53.340
NICHOLS: That's not important.

01:00:53.420 --> 01:00:55.210
We're just trying to figure out
what happened.

01:00:55.290 --> 01:00:57.670
Vic killed him.

01:00:57.750 --> 01:00:59.210
What?

01:00:59.290 --> 01:01:00.460
- GRANT: Ah, come on, man.
- JONAS: Melinda, come on.

01:01:00.540 --> 01:01:02.500
- (scoffs) Jesus.
- MELINDA: Huh?

01:01:02.590 --> 01:01:04.210
You killed him.

01:01:04.290 --> 01:01:06.630
- VIC: Melinda…
- MELINDA: Didn't you?

01:01:06.710 --> 01:01:08.090
- Melinda. -Stop it.
- Okay, nah.

01:01:08.170 --> 01:01:09.710
- MELINDA: Didn't you?
- Melinda, calm down.

01:01:09.790 --> 01:01:11.920
You probably hit him over the head
and drowned him.

01:01:12.000 --> 01:01:13.880
GRANT:
Okay, yeah, it's really...

01:01:13.960 --> 01:01:14.960
My wife's upset.

01:01:15.040 --> 01:01:17.630
I'm not fucking upset!
You fucking killed him!

01:01:17.710 --> 01:01:19.210
- GRANT: Whoa, oh.
- NICHOLS: Mrs. Van Allen,

01:01:19.290 --> 01:01:20.960
would you like to speak privately?

01:01:24.460 --> 01:01:26.290
NICHOLS:
Get an account from the rest of them.

01:01:26.380 --> 01:01:28.750
GRANT (quietly): Goddamn it...

01:01:30.750 --> 01:01:32.590
(door closes)

01:01:32.670 --> 01:01:34.040
CLARK: Who pulled him out?

01:01:34.130 --> 01:01:36.290
- We all did. -We all did.
- JEFF: We all pulled him out.

01:01:36.380 --> 01:01:38.340
Vic and I did CPR.

01:01:38.420 --> 01:01:39.750
But, um...

01:01:39.840 --> 01:01:43.090
Charlie got banged
against the edge of the pool,

01:01:43.170 --> 01:01:46.340
um, but Don was lifting him.

01:01:48.340 --> 01:01:50.670
That didn't affect the death.

01:01:51.750 --> 01:01:53.710
Didn't help.

01:01:53.790 --> 01:01:57.130
And how long did you attempt
to revive him, Mr. Van Allen?

01:01:57.210 --> 01:01:59.540
As long as we had any hope
he was still alive.

01:01:59.630 --> 01:02:01.210
- We alternated.
- Hmm.

01:02:01.290 --> 01:02:03.590
He was dead in the pool.

01:02:03.670 --> 01:02:04.960
(door opens)

01:02:05.040 --> 01:02:06.880
- NICHOLS: Mr. Van Allen.
- Yeah.

01:02:06.960 --> 01:02:09.340
- Would you follow me in here, please?
- Sure.

01:02:11.250 --> 01:02:15.420
I'd like to talk to Chief Nichols, too,
please, privately.

01:02:21.540 --> 01:02:23.630
(sniffs)

01:02:24.960 --> 01:02:27.000
Was your wife sleeping with Mr. De Lisle?

01:02:29.540 --> 01:02:31.500
I don't know.

01:02:31.590 --> 01:02:33.710
I don't ask her those type of questions.

01:02:34.790 --> 01:02:38.090
Well, that's strange. Why is that?

01:02:38.170 --> 01:02:40.340
'Cause I don't feel the need
to dictate her choices.

01:02:40.420 --> 01:02:42.790
I accept her and love her for who she is.

01:02:44.000 --> 01:02:46.540
Well, she's currently
accusing you of murder.

01:02:46.630 --> 01:02:49.040
I didn't say she was always rational.

01:02:49.130 --> 01:02:50.340
NICHOLS: Hmm.

01:02:52.750 --> 01:02:55.500
Did you kill Mr. De Lisle?

01:02:56.590 --> 01:02:58.000
No.

01:02:58.090 --> 01:03:00.420
When Grant and I went inside,
it was raining quite heavily.

01:03:00.500 --> 01:03:03.960
Mr. De Lisle was clinging
to the deep end of the pool.

01:03:04.040 --> 01:03:07.460
I didn't get the sense
he was a very strong swimmer.

01:03:07.540 --> 01:03:09.750
Grant and I went in.

01:03:09.840 --> 01:03:12.170
I tried to steal a cookie.

01:03:12.250 --> 01:03:13.290
(door opens)

01:03:15.170 --> 01:03:17.250
Good night.

01:03:20.920 --> 01:03:22.710
(Jonas sighs)

01:03:22.790 --> 01:03:24.170
Hey.

01:03:24.250 --> 01:03:26.290
Listen, get some rest.

01:03:26.380 --> 01:03:27.630
Call me if you need anything.

01:03:27.710 --> 01:03:29.250
I will.

01:03:29.340 --> 01:03:31.880
Don't let this get you down, all right?

01:03:31.960 --> 01:03:33.790
Get him down? He should be down.

01:03:33.880 --> 01:03:36.290
He should be at the bottom
of that fucking pool.

01:03:39.380 --> 01:03:40.790
(Jonas sighs)

