01:04:01.250 --> 01:04:03.250
(Melinda grunting, mutters)

01:04:05.340 --> 01:04:07.340
(sobs)

01:04:09.420 --> 01:04:11.130
(sniffling)

01:04:14.880 --> 01:04:16.710
VIC: Thank you so much.

01:04:16.790 --> 01:04:18.210
You know what? Just keep this.

01:04:18.290 --> 01:04:19.540
Okay? Thanks.

01:04:19.630 --> 01:04:21.250
Watch out for the dog.

01:04:22.590 --> 01:04:24.380
Thank you.

01:04:40.290 --> 01:04:42.500
(Vic sighs)

01:04:43.590 --> 01:04:45.920
So, what now?

01:04:46.000 --> 01:04:47.670
You want a divorce?

01:04:51.790 --> 01:04:55.290
I can't stand that you think
you're this much smarter than me.

01:04:55.380 --> 01:04:57.000
I don't think that.

01:05:02.130 --> 01:05:05.590
If you think I killed Charlie...

01:05:07.000 --> 01:05:09.250
...aren't you frightened of me?

01:05:11.540 --> 01:05:13.170
No.

01:05:13.250 --> 01:05:15.210
Why not?

01:05:15.290 --> 01:05:18.250
'Cause I'm the thing you killed for.

01:05:20.790 --> 01:05:23.130
Hmm.

